        "subject": "LU-2212 ptlrpc: load crc32c module before mount",
        "message": "LU-2212 ptlrpc: load crc32c module before mount\n\nDue to the use of cryptoapi not loading the crc32c module by module\nsymbols, the crc32c algorithm is not available by default.  Force\nload the module at mount time so that it is available (if supported).\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I0276b1a51704e4e8256a6a4bbe3ae9180105cab0\n"
      },
